# EduVance AI — Backend

FastAPI backend for EduVance AI: video/document ingestion, EasyOCR, Whisper
transcription, and Phi-3-mini reasoning (via Hugging Face Inference API).

See the deployment guide for required secrets (HF_TOKEN, DATABASE_URL,
MINIO_ENDPOINT/MINIO_ACCESS_KEY/MINIO_SECRET_KEY, JWT secret, etc).
